 at King Birger's estate. The dukes captured and imprisoned Birger and his wife in Nykoping Castle's dungeon. Duke Eric then gained power over Sweden.","jurisdictionLevel":1},{"id":1357048,"age":103,"year":"1318","julianDay":2202450,"description":"Peasants revolted against King.","jurisdictionLevel":1}],"lifeSummary":"When Matts Anbjornsson was born about 1215, in Skaraborg, Sweden, his father, Ambjorn Birgersson, was 32 and his mother, Female Unknown (wife of Ambjorn Birgersson), was 27. He married Mrs. Matts Ambjornsson. They were the parents of at least 3 sons."},"et":{"abt 1215–":"umbes 1215–Surnud","1215–Male":"1215–Surnud","1225–Female":"1225–Surnud","1250–Male":"1250–Surnud","1252–Male":"1252–Surnud","1185–Male":"1185–Surnud","1190–Female":"1190–Surnud","Abt 1252":"umbes 1252","1190":"1190","abt 1215":"umbes 1215","Abt 1250":"umbes 1250","1215":"1215","1225":"1225","1252":"1252","1185":"1185","1250":"1250","abt. 1250":"umbes 1250","1318":"1318","1306":"1306","Vinsarp, Dalum, Skaraborg, Sweden":"Västergötland, Rootsi","Vinstorpa, Skaraborg, Sweden":"Skaraborg, Rootsi"},"fi":{"abt 1215–":"noin 1215–Kuollut","1215–Male":"1215–Kuollut","1225–Female":"1225–Kuollut","1250–Male":"1250–Kuollut","1252–Male":"1252–Kuollut","1185–Male":"1185–Kuollut","1190–Female":"1190–Kuollut","Abt 1252":"noin 1252","1190":"1190","abt 1215":"noin 1215","Abt 1250":"noin 1250","1215":"1215","1225":"1225","1252":"1252","1185":"1185","1250":"1250","abt. 1250":"noin 1250","1318":"1318","1306":"1306","Vinsarp, Dalum, Skaraborg, Sweden":"Västergötland, Ruotsi","Vinstorpa, Skaraborg, Sweden":"Skaraborg, Ruotsi"},"fr":{"abt 1215–":"environ 1215–Décédé","1215–Male":"1215–Décédé","1225–Female":"1225–Décédée","1250–Male":"1250–Décédé","1252–Male":"1252–Décédé","1185–Male":"1185–Décédé","1190–Female":"1190–Décédée","Abt 1252":"environ 1252","1190":"1190","abt 1215":"environ 1215","Abt 1250":"environ 1250","1215":"1215","1225":"1225","1252":"1252","1185":"1185","1250":"1250","abt. 1250":"environ 12